{
  "info": {
    "name": "Krypton E-commerce — Carrito",
    "description": "Carrito de compras de Krypton.\n\nFlujo sugerido:\n1. Corrés 'Login (admin)' → guarda el JWT en {{adminToken}}.\n2. Creás categoría y producto de prueba (necesitás datos en el catálogo).\n3. Registrás un cliente y hacés 'Login (cliente)' → guarda el JWT en {{clientToken}}.\n4. Todos los endpoints de /api/cart usan {{clientToken}} (cualquier usuario autenticado puede operar su carrito).\n5. 'Add item' guarda {{itemId}} para encadenar update/delete.\n\nBase URL por defecto: http://localhost:8080\nAdmin sembrado: admin@krypton.pe / Admin123!\n\nNotas de comportamiento:\n- El carrito se crea automáticamente al primer POST /api/cart/items (lazy creation).\n- Agregar el mismo producto dos veces SUMA cantidades (merge semántico, no duplica).\n- quantity > stock → 422. Producto inactivo → 404. quantity ≤ 0 → 400.\n- DELETE /api/cart es idempotente: devuelve 204 aunque el carrito esté vacío.\n- IDOR: el carrito siempre se carga desde el token; no se puede acceder al carrito de otro usuario.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl",          "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "adminToken",       "value": "" },
    { "key": "clientToken",      "value": "" },
    { "key": "adminEmail",       "value": "admin@krypton.pe" },
    { "key": "adminPassword",    "value": "Admin123!" },
    { "key": "clientEmail",      "value": "cliente@test.pe" },
    { "key": "clientPassword",   "value": "Cliente123!" },
    { "key": "categoryId",       "value": "1" },
    { "key": "productId",        "value": "1" },
    { "key": "itemId",           "value": "1" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Setup — Datos de prueba",
      "description": "Preparación: token admin, categoría, producto, registro y token del cliente. Corré en orden la primera vez.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Login (admin) → guarda adminToken",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('adminToken', res.token);",
                  "  console.log('adminToken guardado');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Login del admin sembrado (V3). Guarda el JWT en {{adminToken}} para crear datos del catálogo."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Create category → guarda categoryId",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('categoryId', res.id);",
                  "  console.log('categoryId =', res.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/categories", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "categories"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Laptops\",\n  \"description\": \"Notebooks y ultrabooks\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Crea la categoría de prueba. Si ya existe (409), editá el nombre. Guarda {{categoryId}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Create product → guarda productId",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('productId', res.id);",
                  "  console.log('productId =', res.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/products", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "products"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"sku\": \"LAP-CART-01\",\n  \"name\": \"Notebook Krypton 14\",\n  \"description\": \"Core i5, 16GB RAM, 512GB SSD\",\n  \"price\": 2999.90,\n  \"stock\": 10,\n  \"imageUrl\": \"https://example.com/lap-cart-01.jpg\",\n  \"categoryId\": {{categoryId}}\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Crea el producto de prueba con stock=10. El productId se guarda en {{productId}} para los requests del carrito."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Register (cliente)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Cliente Tester\",\n  \"email\": \"{{clientEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{clientPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Registra el usuario cliente. 201 si es nuevo, 409 si ya existe (podés saltearte este paso si ya lo creaste antes)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "5. Login (cliente) → guarda clientToken",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('clientToken', res.token);",
                  "  console.log('clientToken guardado');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{clientEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{clientPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Login del cliente. Guarda el JWT en {{clientToken}}. Todos los endpoints de /api/cart usan este token."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Carrito (requiere clientToken)",
      "description": "Los 5 endpoints del carrito. Todos requieren {{clientToken}}. El flujo natural: GET → POST → POST (merge) → PUT → DELETE item → DELETE carrito.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /api/cart — ver carrito",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cart", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "cart"] },
            "description": "Devuelve el carrito del usuario autenticado. Si no existe aún, devuelve 200 con items=[] y total=0 (NO crea el carrito en DB). Respuesta: { cartId, updatedAt, items: [{ itemId, productId, productName, sku, price, quantity, subtotal }], total }."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /api/cart/items — agregar producto → guarda itemId",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.items && res.items.length > 0) {",
                  "  const item = res.items[res.items.length - 1];",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('itemId', item.itemId);",
                  "  console.log('itemId =', item.itemId);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "cart", "items"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"productId\": {{productId}},\n  \"quantity\": 2\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Agrega el producto al carrito. Si el carrito no existe, se crea automáticamente (lazy creation). Responde 201 con el CartResponse actualizado. El test script guarda el itemId del último ítem en {{itemId}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /api/cart/items — mismo producto (merge de cantidades)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "cart", "items"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"productId\": {{productId}},\n  \"quantity\": 1\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Mismo productId que el request anterior. El carrito NO crea una fila duplicada — suma la cantidad al ítem existente (quantity pasa de 2 a 3). Respondé con el CartResponse con quantity=3."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT /api/cart/items/{{itemId}} — actualizar cantidad",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items/{{itemId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "cart", "items", "{{itemId}}"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"quantity\": 5\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Reemplaza la cantidad del ítem {{itemId}} por el valor enviado (no suma — reemplaza). 200 con CartResponse actualizado. 404 si el ítem no existe o pertenece a otro usuario (IDOR). 422 si quantity > stock."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "DELETE /api/cart/items/{{itemId}} — eliminar ítem",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items/{{itemId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "cart", "items", "{{itemId}}"] },
            "description": "Elimina el ítem {{itemId}} del carrito. 204 si ok. 404 si no existe o pertenece a otro usuario."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "DELETE /api/cart — vaciar carrito (idempotente)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cart", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "cart"] },
            "description": "Elimina todos los ítems del carrito. 204 siempre — incluso si el carrito estaba vacío o no existía (idempotente)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Casos de error",
      "description": "Verificación de validaciones y guards del carrito.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "401 — sin token",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cart", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "cart"] },
            "description": "GET sin Authorization header. Debe responder 401 Unauthorized."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "400 — quantity=0 rechazada",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "cart", "items"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"productId\": {{productId}},\n  \"quantity\": 0\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "quantity=0 viola @Min(1). Debe responder 400 Bad Request."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "400 — quantity negativa rechazada",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "cart", "items"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"productId\": {{productId}},\n  \"quantity\": -5\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "quantity=-5 viola @Min(1). Debe responder 400 Bad Request."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "422 — quantity > stock",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "cart", "items"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"productId\": {{productId}},\n  \"quantity\": 9999\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "quantity=9999 supera el stock disponible (10). Debe responder 422 Unprocessable Entity con InsufficientStockException."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "404 — producto inexistente",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "cart", "items"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"productId\": 999999,\n  \"quantity\": 1\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "productId=999999 no existe. Debe responder 404 Not Found."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "404 — ítem de otro usuario (IDOR)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items/{{itemId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "cart", "items", "{{itemId}}"] },
            "description": "Intenta eliminar {{itemId}} que pertenece al cliente, pero usando el token del admin. Debe responder 404 (no se revela la existencia del ítem — IDOR protection)."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
